    <item>
      <title>欧元区经济活动因法国大选风险和制造业衰退而放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/french-business-activity-unexpectedly-weakens-on-election-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于法国提前大选的结果给企业带来压力，欧元区私营部门商业活动的反弹意外失去动力，该地区的制造业经历了今年以来最糟糕的一个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/french-business-activity-unexpectedly-weakens-on-election-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 07:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称中国将要求 Visa 和万事达卡降低交易费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/china-said-to-ask-visa-mastercard-to-cut-transaction-fees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士称，中国正在敦促 Visa 公司和万事达卡公司降低在华银行卡交易费用，以方便外国游客支付。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/china-said-to-ask-visa-mastercard-to-cut-transaction-fees</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 05:23:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
